INSERT INTO `carousel` (`id`, `link`, `graphic`, `text`) VALUES
(1, '_001_001', 'images/champion300.jpg', '<h2>Welcome to The Burdette Cancer Portal</h2><p id="tagline">Information, Resources, and Tools for People Dealing With Cancer.</p><p>We know that thinking about cancer can be worrisome. The good news is that today there are more than 10 million cancer survivors.</p>'),
(2, '_001_004', 'images/healthMatters_300.png', '<h2>IU Cancer Research Interventions</h2><p>Research interventions emphasizing cancer prevention, cancer screening, symptom management practices, and cancer patient caregiver support.</p>'),
(3, '_002', 'images/chromosomes_300.jpg', '<h2>Cancer Basics</h2><p>Your body is made up of trillions of cells. The life cycle of each of your cells is controlled by its genes. Cancer is caused by changes (or mutations) in a cell\'s genes. Researchers have learned that mutations in genes can be caused by risk factors, such as lifestyle or the environment.</p>'),
(4, '_002_005', 'images/chemo_300.png', '<h2>Treatment</h2><p>There are many types of cancer and many treatment options. A treatment plan should be developed based on several factors: type of cancer, stage or how much it has spread, location, and the general health of the patient.</p>'),
(5, '_003', 'images/chairs_300.png', '<h2>Symptom Management</h2><p>Chemotherapy patients often experience side-effect symptoms that can make them feel sick.  Learn techniques for managing side-effect symptoms that can help improve your well-being.</p>'),
(6, '_003_002', 'images/graph_300.png', '<h2>Symptom Reports</h2><p>Use the Symptom Reporting tool to track your progress with managing side-effect symptoms.  History graphs and customized symptom management advice are available with symptom reporting.</p>');
